                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10203" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2577</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">227 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">成本“菲”降不可 竞争力“达”势如虹 ——菲达环保的降本增竞之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Lowering Costs, Rising Competitiveness  — Feida Environmental’s Path to Cost Reduction and Competitive Advantage</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">朱新玲，车梓惠，张秋瑾，刘燕婷</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">武汉科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">浙江菲达环保科技股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">26 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">成本管理；核心竞争力；菲达环保</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Cost Management; Core Competitiveness; Feida Environmental</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在可持续发展战略深化与环保设备行业加速转型的背景下，行业竞争日益激烈，原材料价格波动频繁，成本管控能力成为影响环保企业可持续发展的关键因素。菲达环保作为大气污染治理装备领域的知名企业，原本就存在成本劣势，如今受行业形势影响，其核心竞争力受到显著冲击。为全面提升核心竞争力，实现可持续发展的长远目标，菲达环保毅然踏上了成本改革之路。通过实施系统化的成本管理策略，企业从优化供应链、改善成本结构、革新核算平台等多个维度入手，全方位降低成本，显著提升了企业在业务、技术和管理方面的竞争力。本案例以菲达环保成本改革为主线，系统探讨环保设备制造企业成本管理优化路径，既有助于分析成本问题、构建应对方案、探寻降本新方向，又能培养学生分析解决问题能力。本案例也为我国环保设备制造企业突破成本困局、实现可持续发展提供了可供参考的实践范式，具有较强实践意义。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Against the background of the deepening sustainable development strategy and the accelerated transformation of the environmental protection equipment industry, industry competition has become increasingly fierce, raw material prices often fluctuate, and cost control ability has become a key factor affecting the sustainable development of environmental protection enterprises. Feida Environmental, as a well-known enterprise in the field of atmospheric pollution control equipment, originally had a cost disadvantage, and now, affected by the industry situation, its core competitiveness has been significantly impacted. In order to comprehensively enhance its core competitiveness and achieve its long-term goal of sustainable development, Feida Environmental has resolutely embarked on the path of cost reform. By implementing a systematic cost management strategy, the enterprise has started from multiple aspects such as optimizing the supply chain, improving the cost structure, and innovating the accounting platform to reduce costs in an all-round way, and has significantly enhanced its competitiveness in business, technology and management. This case takes the cost reform of Feida Environmental as the main line to systematically explore the cost management optimization path for environmental protection equipment manufacturing enterprises. It not only helps to analyze cost problems, build response plans, and find new directions for cost reduction, but also helps to develop students&#39; ability to analyze and solve problems. This case also provides a practical paradigm for environmental protection equipment manufacturing enterprises in China to break through the cost dilemma and achieve sustainable development, and has strong practical significance.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略成本管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">（1）识别企业存在的成本问题
（2）掌握降低成本的方式
（3）分析成本管理与核心竞争力的关系</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-12</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
